Listen, maybe we got off to a bad start.

819
01:32:30,582 --> 01:32:35,671
如果我们要合作 该互相了解一下
We're going to work together. We should get to know each other.

820
01:32:35,837 --> 01:32:40,133
你打网球吗? 网球? 你打网球吗?
Do you play tennis? Tennis? Do you play tennis?

821
01:32:40,300 --> 01:32:44,638
- 我有打网球  - 来一次聚会如何?
- Yeah, I play tennis.  - How about we get together?

822
01:32:44,805 --> 01:32:48,100
下星期? 上班前好吗?
Next week? Hour before we startwork?

823
01:32:55,399 --> 01:32:57,401
- 杰克?  - 是的
- Jack?  - Yeah.

824
01:32:58,110 --> 01:33:01,780
电脑盗窃是个严重的罪行
Computer theft is a serious crime.

825
01:33:05,659 --> 01:33:09,121
违反宪法的罪行也是一样
So are crimes against the Constitution.

826
01:33:10,622 --> 01:33:12,708
混蛋!
Son of a bitch!

827
01:33:24,761 --> 01:33:26,638
混蛋!
Son of a bitch!

828
01:33:31,059 --> 01:33:33,145
来吧 来吧
Come on, come on.

829
01:33:35,564 --> 01:33:37,649
祁洛
Clark.

830
01:33:49,703 --> 01:33:51,204
是的
Yeah.

831
01:34:13,393 --> 01:34:16,563
朋友 你要坐牢了
You'll go to jail, pal.

832
01:34:16,730 --> 01:34:20,275
那是什么? 你以为你抓到什么?
What is that? What do you think you have there?

833
01:34:20,442 --> 01:34:22,110
你犯了法
You broke the law.

834
01:34:23,153 --> 01:34:27,240
你真是个白痴
You are such a Boy Scout.

835
01:34:27,407 --> 01:34:30,786
看你你眼中只有黑与白
Look at you. You see everything in black and white.

836
01:34:30,953 --> 01:34:34,915
不是黑与白 是对与错!
No, not black and white, Ritter. Right and wrong!

837
01:34:35,082 --> 01:34:39,336
- 看到吗? 又来了  - 为何我毫不知情?
- You see? There you go again.  - Why was I kept out of it?

838
01:34:39,503 --> 01:34:43,131
你身陷其中 你到过国会
You're neck deep in it. You went before Congress.

839
01:34:43,298 --> 01:34:46,301
获得拨款 你还发假誓
You got the money for it. You lied under oath...

840
01:34:46,468 --> 01:34:50,931
- 我没有向国会说谎!  - 你向他们说不会有军队
- I never lied to Congress!  - You told them no troops.

841
