Keep pushing forward. We'll trap them.

873
01:38:32,277 --> 01:38:35,781
他从不轻易相信
Never, though, was he deluded into thinking that one man

874
01:38:35,947 --> 01:38:38,867
个人可以救治世界
could solve the ills of the world.

875
01:38:39,493 --> 01:38:43,664
一直作为队中的军人 他出战南太平洋
Always the soldier, on the battlefields of the South Pacific,

876
01:38:43,830 --> 01:38:48,919
韩国 越南和华盛顿
Korea, Vietnam and Washington, he fought as part of a unit

877
01:38:49,086 --> 01:38:51,421
去捍卫国家的...
to preserve the ideals...

878
01:38:51,588 --> 01:38:55,050
- 刀子 这是变量 完毕  - ...理念
- Knife, this is Variable, over.  - ...of his nation.

879
01:38:55,217 --> 01:38:57,678
刀子! 这是变量 完毕
Knife! This is Variable, over.

880
01:38:59,054 --> 01:39:03,266
我们把我们友人的躯体 信靠予大地的庇护
To the refuge of the earth, we entrust our friend's body.

881
01:39:03,433 --> 01:39:08,188
把他的灵魂信靠予上主的保佑
To the protection of our God in Heaven, we entrust his soul.

882
01:39:08,355 --> 01:39:12,693
把他的精神和生存原则
To ourselves, we entrust his spirit

883
01:39:12,859 --> 01:39:15,946
信靠予我们
and the principles he lived by.

884
01:39:16,947 --> 01:39:18,949
正文 我们会怀念你
We're gonna miss you, James.

885
01:39:41,638 --> 01:39:44,599
变量 这是刀子 完毕
Variable, this is Knife, over.

886
01:39:44,766 --> 01:39:47,769
变量 这是刀子 完毕
Variable, this is Knife, over.

887
01:39:47,936 --> 01:39:51,440
变量 我接收不到 我们遇到猛烈袭击
Variable, I am not receiving. We are under heavy attack.

888
01:39:51,606 --> 01:39:54,985
- 需要空中支援 完毕  - 快 快 快!
- Need air support, over.  - Go, go, go!

889
01:40:16,173 --> 01:40:20,010
变量 这是刀子 完毕! 转!
Variable, this is Knife, over! Switch!

890
01:40:52,376 --> 01:40:56,380
变量 这是刀子! 你到底到哪里?
Variable, this is Knife! Where the hell are you?

891
01:41:11,478 --> 01:41:15,107
伸出你们的手来
Present arms.

892
01:41:17,943 --> 01:41:22,447
我代表全国致以我们的哀悼
On behalf of a grateful nation, our condolences.

893
01:41:22,614 --> 01:41:26,368
- 他是个了不起的爱国者  - 谢谢
- He was a very great patriot.  - Thank you.

894
01:41:34,876 --> 01:41:37,004
击中目标
All aim.

895
01:42:04,364 --> 01:42:06,908
- 你好?  - 霍珍找赖杰克博士
- Hello?  - Jean Fowler for Dr Jack Ryan.

896
01:42:07,075 --> 01:42:08,785
我是
This is he.

897
01:42:08,952 --> 01:42:12,331
杰克? 你要听一听这个
Jack? You've got to hear this.

898
01:42:12,497 --> 01:42:15,083
今早接收到的
Picked it up this morning.

899
01:42:15,250 --> 01:42:21,173
变量 这是刀子 我们遇到袭击 需要空中支援
Variable, this is Knife. We are under attack, need air support.

900
01:42:21,340 --> 01:42:24,635
变量 这是刀子 你到底在哪里?
Variable, this is Knife, where the hell are you?

901
01:42:25,427 --> 01:42:28,347
你想我怎样处理这事?
Jack, what do you want me to do with this?

902
01:42:29,431 --> 01:42:33,810
制一条副声带 制十条
Make a copy, Jean. Make ten copies.

903
01:42:33,977 --> 01:42:37,064
尽快给我送过来 谢谢
Get them to me as quick as you can. Thanks.

904
01:42:39,566 --> 01:42:44,738
天啊 他们要把那些人留在那里
Jesus. They're going to leave those guys down there.

905
01:43:27,322 --> 01:43:33,412
他正乘美航915班机 会在晚上7点50分抵达波哥大
He's on American 915. He'll be in Bogota 7:50 pm.

906
01:43:45,340 --> 01:43:47,342
- 什么事?  - 我是雷
- Yeah?  - It's Ritter.

907
01:43:47,509 --> 01:43:51,221
- 你他妈的去了哪里?  - 我们有困难
- Where the fuck have you been?  - We have a problem.

908
01:43:51,388 --> 01:43:54,308
我们有大灾难! 我联络不到我的手下
We've got a disaster! I can't get through to my men.

909
01:43:55,017 --> 01:43:58,520
我们要关掉卫星通讯
We had to shut down the satellite link.

910
01:43:59,938 --> 01:44:02,941
- 祁洛?  - 你要什么?
- Clark?  - You had to what?

911
01:44:04,276 --> 01:44:10,198
这是赖 他发现一切 还恐吓要通知国会
It's Ryan. He found out everything. He threatened to walk up the Hill

912
01:44:10,365 --> 01:44:13,285
如果我们不停止行动
if we didn't shut down the operation.

913
01:44:13,452 --> 01:44:19,207
好的 停止吧 给我一点空间让我的手下脱险
OK. It's shut down. Just give me some air and my men are out of there.

914
01:44:20,667 --> 01:44:26,923
可能你没留心听我说 没有空间了 我们被切断
Clark, maybe you're not hearing me. There is no air. We are shut down.

915
01:44:28,675 --> 01:44:32,095
我正在机上 我要杀死他
I'm on a plane. I'm gonna kill him.

916
01:44:33,472 --> 01:44:35,557
雷?
Ritter?

917
01:44:37,309 --> 01:44:39,853
别上飞机 他要来找你
Don't get on a plane. He's coming to you.

918
01:44:40,020 --> 01:44:44,024
美国航空7点50分 没有保安
American Airlines at 19:50 hours with no security.

919
01:44:44,191 --> 01:44:48,445
- 你是谁?  - 国家安全顾问葛哲时
- Who is this?  - National Security Advisor Cutter.

920
01:44:48,612 --> 01:44:51,615
赖一走我们就恢复通讯
Once Ryan's gone, we're back on line.

921
01:44:52,199 --> 01:44:54,284
你明白吗?
You understand?

922
01:44:55,410 --> 01:44:57,746
明白
Yes, sir.

923
01:46:18,160 --> 01:46:19,786
祁洛
Clark.

924
01:46:19,953 --> 01:46:21,788
- 天啊!  - 上车
- Jesus!  - Get in the van.

925
01:46:21,955 --> 01:46:24,291
别这样 我来找你的
Don't be an asshole, I came to find you.

926
01:46:24,458 --> 01:46:26,793
你找到我了 上车
You found me. Get in.

927
01:46:28,086 --> 01:46:29,588
好吧
Alright.

928
01:46:30,922 --> 01:46:32,633
坐到方向盘后
Behind the wheel.

929
01:46:34,134 --> 01:46:36,094
祁洛
Clark.

930
01:46:37,012 --> 01:46:39,514
开车
Drive.

931
01:47:06,708 --> 01:47:09,336
- 雷  - 赖死了
- Ritter.  - Ryan's dead.

932
01:47:11,254 --> 01:47:12,464
怎么会?
How?

933
01:47:13,674 --> 01:47:16,843
我杀了他 再启动卫星吧
I killed him. Turn the op back on.

934
01:47:20,013 --> 01:47:25,143
你叫我干掉赖 我们再恢复合作 是吗?
You said get rid of Ryan and we're back in business, right?

935
01:47:50,168 --> 01:47:52,337
你来这里干什么?
What the hell are you doing here?

936
01:47:54,715 --> 01:47:57,926
我来帮你救你的手下
I came to help you get those guys out.

937
01:47:59,469 --> 01:48:02,180
你可以怎样帮我?
What can you do to help me?

938
01:48:07,728 --> 01:48:10,605
你需要什么?
What do you need?

939
01:48:10,772 --> 01:48:12,357
一架直升机
A helicopter.

940
01:48:14,735 --> 01:48:17,529
一架直升机
A helicopter.

941
01:48:25,579 --> 01:48:26,955
不 谢谢
No, thank you.

942
01:48:29,958 --> 01:48:33,170
- 这是"欢乐时光" 吗?  - 永远都是"欢乐时光"
- Is this happy hour?  - It's always happy hour.

943
01:48:33,337 --> 01:48:37,132
- 你的机师拥有这个地方?  - 他住在这里
- Your pilot owns this joint?  - He lives here.

944
01:48:42,638 --> 01:48:44,097
他在这里
Here he is.

945
01:48:55,192 --> 01:48:57,110
- 早安  - 早安
- Morning.  - Morning.

946
01:48:57,277 --> 01:49:00,113
你早 我想租那架直升机
Morning. I'm here to rent the Huey.

947
01:49:00,280 --> 01:49:04,868
抱歉 我们不再出租 但可以出售
Sorry, we don't rent it any more. But it is for sale.

948
01:49:05,911 --> 01:49:07,955
多少钱?
How much is it?

949
01:49:09,247 --> 01:49:11,917
两百万元
Two million dollars.

950
01:49:16,421 --> 01:49:20,008
我的机师和我要作飞行测试
My pilot and I would have to do a test flight.

951
01:49:20,175 --> 01:49:23,387
可以 你只需留下订金
Of course. You just have to leave a deposit.

952
01:49:25,055 --> 01:49:26,974
要多少?
How much is that?

953
01:49:27,140 --> 01:49:28,767
两百万元
Two million dollars.

954
01:49:34,439 --> 01:49:37,776
你收公司支票吗?
Would you take a company cheque?

955
01:49:44,283 --> 01:49:45,909
收
Yes.

956
01:49:53,709 --> 01:49:58,005
- 我们来吧  - 她是大混蛋 是吗?
- Here we go.  - Big son of a bitch, ain't she?

957
01:49:59,631 --> 01:50:04,094
- 你花过时间在这种类型吗?  - 九点
- Do you have any time in this type?  - Nine o'clock.

958
01:50:13,979 --> 01:50:19,943
- 别上我的直升机  - 不 是我的直升机 走吧
- Get out of my chopper.  - No. My chopper. Let's go.

959
01:50:40,714 --> 01:50:43,925
他们最后一次通讯在这个位置
Their last communication put them here.

960
01:50:45,135 --> 01:50:50,265
