The closest extraction point is here, in this gorge.

961
01:50:51,266 --> 01:50:52,893
我知道了
I got it.

962
01:51:12,496 --> 01:51:16,208
- 下面那个是尸体吗?  - 是的
- Is that a body down there?  - Yeah.

963
01:51:18,085 --> 01:51:21,797
- 我们其中一个?  - 我其中一个
- One of ours?  - One of mine.

964
01:51:25,175 --> 01:51:29,972
找一个降落地点 我们去找其他人
Find a place to set her down. We'll look for the others.

965
01:52:13,140 --> 01:52:17,853
没地方逃走 没地方躲藏
Nowhere to run to. No place to hide.

966
01:52:18,020 --> 01:52:23,275
到处都有走向河那边的血路
Blood trails everywhere. They all lead to the river.

967
01:52:36,496 --> 01:52:40,626
这些是我们从空中看到的瀑布
These are the falls we saw from the air.

968
01:52:40,792 --> 01:52:44,546
尸体该在下面大概五十米
The bodies should be about 50 metres down.

969
01:52:56,350 --> 01:53:01,438
