973
01:53:14,284 --> 01:53:16,662
是我的错
It's my fault.

974
01:53:20,958 --> 01:53:23,543
是我的错
It's my fault.

975
01:53:35,222 --> 01:53:39,309
最后一次袭击时 我跟尖头通过话
I was on point when the last attack came.

976
01:53:40,352 --> 01:53:42,688
距离超过一哩
Over a mile away.

977
01:53:43,772 --> 01:53:46,066
我回来时已经完了
By the time I got back, it was over.

978
01:53:47,526 --> 01:53:50,737
他们带走了奥苏队长
They were taking the Captain and Oso.

979
01:53:51,530 --> 01:53:52,906
其他人呢?
The others?

980
01:53:54,616 --> 01:53:56,368
我埋藏了他们
I buried them.

981
01:54:05,210 --> 01:54:07,379
然后回去了
Road to the town.

982
01:54:07,546 --> 01:54:10,882
他们在这里押走他们 到处都是血
They loaded the prisoners here. Blood everywhere.

983
01:54:11,049 --> 01:54:14,845
- 天晓得他们现在在哪里  - 颜力图知道
- God knows where they are now.  - Escobedo knows.

984
01:54:15,012 --> 01:54:18,307
你想怎么样? 敲他的门?
What are you going to do? Knock on his door?

985
01:54:24,938 --> 01:54:29,985
你早 我想见颜力图 我没有预约
Morning. I'd like to see Ernesto Escobedo. I have no appointment.

986
01:54:31,403 --> 01:54:33,614
谢谢
Gracias.

987
01:54:43,457 --> 01:54:45,626
好的
OK.

988
01:54:47,419 --> 01:54:49,379
举起手来
Hands up.

989
01:54:50,005 --> 01:54:51,965
举起手来!
Hands up!

990
01:54:53,508 --> 01:54:55,844
钱包
Wallet.

991
01:55:00,223 --> 01:55:03,018
是个录音机
It's a tape recorder.

992
01:55:06,563 --> 01:55:09,149
他进去了
He's in.

993
01:55:11,693 --> 01:55:14,696
小鸟 这是变量 完毕
Bird, this is Variable, over.

994
01:55:16,615 --> 01:55:20,535
小鸟 这是变量 完毕
Bird, this is Variable, over.

995
01:55:36,468 --> 01:55:40,389
赖博士 请进
Dr Ryan. Come in.

996
01:55:54,027 --> 01:55:58,115
坐下 有什么为你效劳?
Sit down. What can I do for you?

997
01:55:59,366 --> 01:56:05,080
我不知道该找谁 我有一个难题
I didn't know who else to turn to. I have a problem.

998
01:56:06,290 --> 01:56:10,002
我有一个朋友 是一个咖啡买家和他的助手
An associate of mine, a coffee buyer and his assistant,

999
01:56:10,168 --> 01:56:13,088
来了这里公干
were on a business trip in this area.

1000
01:56:13,255 --> 01:56:17,050
他们昨天失踪了 我很担心
They unexpectedly disappeared yesterday. I'm very concerned.

1001
01:56:17,217 --> 01:56:19,428
咖啡买家?
Coffee buyer?

1002
01:56:19,594 --> 01:56:22,347
我很想寻回他们
It's very important to me to find them.

1003
01:56:22,514 --> 01:56:25,767
收买咖啡是越来越危险的生意
Coffee buying is becoming a dangerous business.

1004
01:56:26,935 --> 01:56:31,732
是的 那是为夏彼得做的
Yes. Well, it was for Peter Hardin.

1005
01:56:34,693 --> 01:56:38,238
- 谁?  - 他是连度咖啡的顾客
- Who?  - He was a client of Lindo Coffee.

1006
01:56:38,405 --> 01:56:43,201
- 连度咖啡有很多顾客  - 你一定有听过这一个
- Lindo Coffee has many clients.  - You must have heard of this one.

1007
01:56:43,368 --> 01:56:47,205
他欠了你公司一大笔钱
He owed your company a great deal of money.

1008
01:56:47,372 --> 01:56:51,376
我要跟会计谈一下
Well, I'll have to talk to accounting about that.

1009
01:56:52,753 --> 01:56:55,255
六亿五千万元
$650 million.

1010
01:56:58,342 --> 01:57:00,594
和零钱
And change.

1011
01:57:01,970 --> 01:57:07,059
你是否提议帮我收烂帐?
Are you offering to help me with the collection of an unpaid debt?

1012
01:57:07,225 --> 01:57:10,354
- 不是  - 你在提议什么?
- No.  - What are you offering?

1013
01:57:11,647 --> 01:57:16,318
一项交易 郭菲力出卖了你
Atrade. Felix Cortez has sold you out.

1014
01:57:16,485 --> 01:57:19,112
他会杀你和你的家人
His next move is to murder you, your family,

1015
01:57:19,279 --> 01:57:20,948
然后接管集团
and take over the cartel.

1016
01:57:21,114 --> 01:57:23,075
我的录音机在哪里?
Where's my tape recorder?

1017
01:57:29,539 --> 01:57:31,500
播放那段带子
Play the tape.

1018
01:58:05,200 --> 01:58:07,494
快走
Let's move.

1019
01:58:36,940 --> 01:58:40,319
我想你见我的新朋友 赖博士
I'd like you to meet my new friend, Dr Ryan.

1020
01:58:40,485 --> 01:58:43,780
"医生"? 为什么? 有人病了?
Doctor? Why? Is somebody sick?

1021
01:58:57,169 --> 01:58:58,879
他想要什么?
What does he want?

1022
01:59:00,922 --> 01:59:04,384
他的朋友们平安返回
The safe return of his associates.

1023
01:59:04,551 --> 01:59:08,805
用什么来交换?
And what does he offer us in return?

1024
01:59:08,972 --> 01:59:11,475
你
You.

1025
01:59:17,147 --> 01:59:21,526
这个人对你说的都是谎话 他靠说谎维生
Whatever this man has told you is a lie. He lies for a living.

1026
01:59:21,693 --> 01:59:26,323
他做情报工作 你也做情报工作!
He's in the intelligence business. You're in the intelligence business!

1027
01:59:32,704 --> 01:59:35,666
你处置了那些小鱼
You've taken care of the little fish.

1028
01:59:35,832 --> 01:59:38,543
我会处置漏网的那一条
I will take care of the one that got away.

1029
01:59:38,710 --> 01:59:43,423
颜力图一走 我就可以帮你
Once Escobedo is gone, I will be in a position to help you.

1030
01:59:43,590 --> 01:59:47,803
问题是...
So, the question is...

1031
01:59:49,137 --> 01:59:51,640
...我该如何处置你?
...what am I supposed to do with you?

1032
01:59:54,726 --> 01:59:57,771
我该用这支棒杀死你!
Well? I guess I'm supposed to kill you with this bat!

1033
02:00:06,280 --> 02:00:08,699
起来
Get up.

1034
02:00:13,245 --> 02:00:17,582
戏剧性的扫荡 大幅减量 不再有暴力...
Dramatic seizures. Drastic reductions, no more violence...

1035
02:00:17,749 --> 02:00:21,128
你会得到胜利
You'll have your victory.

1036
02:00:21,795 --> 02:00:23,505
以什么来交换?
In return for what?

1037
02:01:03,712 --> 02:01:05,797
- 他们在哪里?  - 在这里
- Where are they?  - They're here.

1038
02:01:07,716 --> 02:01:12,763
那美国人杀死了颜力图! 我们快走!
Kill the plant. The American killed Ernesto! Let's go!

1039
02:02:00,519 --> 02:02:02,938
小鸟找变量 完毕
Bird to Variable, over.

1040
02:02:16,034 --> 02:02:17,619
小鸟 这是变量
Bird, this is Variable.

1041
02:02:17,786 --> 02:02:20,122
你到底在哪里?
Where the hell are you?

1042
02:02:20,289 --> 02:02:25,043
我在村落以南约五公里处盘旋
I'm cruising about five clicks south of the village.

1043
02:02:25,961 --> 02:02:30,048
- 留在那里 我再联络你  - 收到
- Stay there. I'll get back to you.  - Roger that.

1044
02:02:41,893 --> 02:02:44,730
- 没有人  - 那些囚犯!
- No one.  - The prisoners!

1045
02:03:31,234 --> 02:03:34,529
来吧 孩子 我们快走
Come on, guys. Let's go, son.

1046
02:03:35,530 --> 02:03:38,325
我们要回家了
We're going home, boys.

1047
02:04:51,315 --> 02:04:54,067
到连度咖啡厂接我们
Pick us up at the Lindo Coffee factory.

1048
02:06:30,497 --> 02:06:34,459
不单我可以向传媒揭发你 士兵也可以
Not only can I expose you to the press, so can the soldiers.

1049
02:06:34,626 --> 02:06:41,341
你可想跟法庭和记者冒险?
Do you want to take your chances with the courts and the reporters?

1050
02:06:41,508 --> 02:06:46,179
结束你总司令的政治生涯?
Do you want to end the career of your commander in chief?

1051
02:07:30,182 --> 02:07:32,517
我们走!
Let's go!

1052
02:07:59,586 --> 02:08:03,090
快上来! 我们要走了!
Get your asses in here! Come on, we got to go!

1053
02:08:06,093 --> 02:08:08,345
来吧!
Come on!

1054
02:08:15,018 --> 02:08:17,354
慢着! 我们要等赖!
Hold it! We wait for Ryan!

1055
02:08:17,521 --> 02:08:19,564
什么? 我们要走了!
Yeah? We're out of here!

1056
02:08:26,822 --> 02:08:29,950
低飞! 他在下面!
Set it down! He's down there!

1057
02:08:42,045 --> 02:08:43,714
来吧!
Come on!

1058
02:09:03,025 --> 02:09:04,860
我抓到你!
I've got you!

1059
02:09:11,742 --> 02:09:14,286
蔡维斯 掩护我!
Chavez, cover me!

1060
02:09:23,128 --> 02:09:26,506
你的手 把你的手给我!
Your hand. Give me your hand!

1061
02:10:32,030 --> 02:10:35,158
总统现在见你
The President will see you now, sir.

1062
02:10:47,421 --> 02:10:50,757
杰克! 你到来真好
Jack! I'm glad you're here.

1063
02:10:51,925 --> 02:10:56,054
坐下 要喝点什么?
Sit down. Can I get you anything?

1064
02:10:56,221 --> 02:10:58,557
不用了
No.

1065
02:10:58,724 --> 02:11:03,020
- 来吧 坐下  - 我宁愿站着
- Come on, sit down.  - I would prefer to stand, sir.

1066
02:11:05,105 --> 02:11:11,612
这里有一些事情 我正开始留意到
Some things have gone on here that I'm just becoming aware of.

1067
02:11:11,778 --> 02:11:16,033
我像你一样一直毫不知情
I was kept in the dark, as you were, for a very long time.

1068
02:11:16,199 --> 02:11:19,453
- 麻烦的事情  - 是的
- Troubling things.  - Yeah.

1069
02:11:19,620 --> 02:11:23,957
现在我们要处理它们 看谁要负责
Now we have to sort them out, figure out who is responsible for what

1070
02:11:24,124 --> 02:11:27,878
和怎样处置它 我们还要小心行事
and what to do about it. We have to do this very delicately,

1071
02:11:28,045 --> 02:11:31,965
否则人们可能会误会
otherwise people might get the wrong idea.

1072
02:11:32,132 --> 02:11:34,343
我们要说谎
We have to lie.

1073
02:11:35,427 --> 02:11:40,098
- 我有那样说吗?  - 你没有
- Did I say that?  - No, you didn't.

1074
02:11:40,265 --> 02:11:43,935
- 你很生气  - 我很生气
- You're upset.  - I'm upset.

1075
02:11:44,102 --> 02:11:49,650
这是可以谅解的 可介意我给你一点忠告?
It's understandable. Do you mind if I give you a bit of advice?

1076
02:11:49,816 --> 02:11:52,110
你知道这件事 你很聪明
You know this because you're smart.

1077
02:11:52,277 --> 02:11:56,323
当你生气时别作重要的决定
Never make important decisions while you're upset.

1078
02:11:56,490 --> 02:12:02,037
你有 正因为它 美国士兵和平民都死了
You did. American soldiers and civilians are dead because of it.

1079
02:12:02,204 --> 02:12:06,124
- 我没有下命令...  - 你别跟我耍那套!
- I never ordered any...  - No. Don't play that game with me!

1080
02:12:06,291 --> 02:12:10,462
你别装作不知情 而令他们蒙羞!
You won't dishonour their memories by pretending you didn't know!

1081
02:12:10,629 --> 02:12:14,424
- 你竟敢训导...  - 你竟敢?
- How dare you lecture...  - How dare you, sir?

1082
02:12:14,591 --> 02:12:18,470
你竟敢到这儿来 像只疯狗般向我狂吠!
How dare you come here and bark at me like a junkyard dog!

1083
02:12:18,637 --> 02:12:21,974
我是美国总统!
I am the President of the United States!

1084
02:12:25,936 --> 02:12:29,481
这件事令我不好受
It gives me no pleasure to do it, sir.

1085
02:12:29,648 --> 02:12:32,901
作为署理情报局副局长
As Acting Deputy Director of Intelligence it is my duty

1086
02:12:33,068 --> 02:12:37,072
向参议院监督委员会报告这事 是我的职责
to report this matter to the Senate Oversight Committee.

1087
02:12:41,994 --> 02:12:44,162
你不能那样做
You're not going to do that.

1088
02:12:45,914 --> 02:12:47,874
- 我不能?  - 不 不
- I'm not?  - No, no.

1089
02:12:50,127 --> 02:12:54,089
你手上现在有个筹码
You've got yourself a chip in the big game now.

1090
02:12:55,382 --> 02:12:57,592
你大可把它留下来
You're going to tuck that away,

1091
02:12:57,759 --> 02:13:01,346
当你自己有麻烦时
save that for a time when your own ass is on the line.

1092
02:13:01,513 --> 02:13:04,599
就把它拿出来
And then you're going to pull it out.

1093
02:13:04,766 --> 02:13:09,229
我也可以助你换成现金 是吗?
And I'm going to cash it in for you. Right?

1094
02:13:11,023 --> 02:13:14,568
我没有其他事要向你说了
I don't think I have anything more to say to you, sir.

1095
02:13:15,861 --> 02:13:21,325
国家不能再有另一宗丑闻 为了自保
The country can't afford another scandal, Jack. To protect itself,

1096
02:13:21,491 --> 02:13:26,997
它不可让另一宗诡计 影响至高层
it won't allow another deception that goes all the way to the top.

1097
02:13:27,164 --> 02:13:31,043
你要受责 葛和雷也会负上一些责任
You'll take the blame. Cutter and Ritter will take some, too,

1098
02:13:31,209 --> 02:13:34,713
他只是很轻微
but it won't amount to much, a slap on the wrist.

1099
02:13:34,880 --> 02:13:40,010
然后到讲学圈子赚时薪二万元
Then $20,000 an hour on the lecture circuit.

1100
02:13:40,177 --> 02:13:43,972
其余的责任将落在纪身上
The rest of the blame will fall on Greer.

1101
02:13:44,139 --> 02:13:48,101
不错 你会带着他下台
Yeah, you'll take him down with you.

1102
02:13:48,268 --> 02:13:50,979
你会摧毁他的名誉
You'll destroy his reputation.

1103
02:13:51,146 --> 02:13:56,652
但只会到那个地步 像古老的波托马克二步舞
But that's as far as it will go. The old Potomac two-step, Jack.

1104
02:13:59,488 --> 02:14:03,325
对不起总统先生 我不跳舞的
I'm sorry, Mr President, I don't dance.

1105
02:14:26,348 --> 02:14:28,934
赖 你有时间吗?
Ryan, have you got a minute?

1106
02:14:29,101 --> 02:14:31,603
没有
No.

1107
02:14:31,770 --> 02:14:34,439
我们要谈一下!
We need to talk!

1108
02:14:34,606 --> 02:14:36,692
赖!
Ryan!

1109
02:15:01,008 --> 02:15:06,722
委员会会议正式开始 主席现在传召赖博士
The Committee will come to order. The Chair will now call Dr Ryan.

1110
02:15:27,659 --> 02:15:31,663
赖博士 感谢你今天出席会议
Dr Ryan, thank you for appearing before the Committee today.

1111
02:15:31,830 --> 02:15:33,540
谢谢你 主席
Thank you, Mr Chairman.

1112
02:15:34,082 --> 02:15:37,544
请起立 举起你的右手
Please stand and raise your right hand.

1113
02:15:40,505 --> 02:15:44,468
你是否严肃地发誓 你即将作出的供词
Do you solemnly swear that the testimony you're about to give

1114
02:15:44,635 --> 02:15:46,428
是事实 全部的事实
is the truth, the whole truth

1115
02:15:46,595 --> 02:15:49,348
只有事实 求主保佑你?
and nothing but the truth, so help you God?

1116
02:15:51,850 --> 02:15:54,019
是的
I do.

1117
02:15:55,604 --> 02:16:00,984
赖博士 你已作出宣誓 请坐
Dr Ryan, you may consider yourself under oath. Please be seated.


